  "summary": "preinstall script executes remote HTA payload via mshta.exe",
  "details": "The package's npm preinstall lifecycle script (preinstall.js) shells out via cmd to invoke Windows mshta.exe against http://fixars.top, causing the installer's machine to fetch and execute remote HTML Application content at install time. The destination is an unrelated bare.top domain, the content is unpinned and mutable, and execution occurs automatically on `npm install` before any user code runs.",
